  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-component=\"article-header\" data-alignment=\"\" data-stack-meta=\"false\"\u003e\u003ch2 data-component=\"text\" data-alias=\"article-header__headline\" data-alignment=\"\" data-theme=\"headline-md\" data-transform=\"\" data-truncate=\"\" id=\"\"\u003eThird \u003cem\u003eDownton Abbey\u003c/em\u003e Movie Will Pay ‘Meaningful’ Tribute to Maggie Smith: ‘The Loss of the Dowager Now Feels Far More Significant’\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv data-alias=\"gutenberg-content__content\" data-social=\"true\" data-component=\"gutenberg-content\" data-template=\"article\" data-inner-width=\"content\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere’s never a dull moment at \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/downton-abbey/\" id=\"auto-tag_downton-abbey_1\" data-tag=\"downton-abbey\"\u003eDownton Abbey\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e, but since Christmas is an especially eventful time for the Crawley family, this feels like the perfect occasion to share a gift — the gift of scoop.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs fans of the hit franchise are painfully aware, the second theatrical film (2022’s \u003cem\u003eDownton Abbey: A New Era\u003c/em\u003e) ended with the death of the Dowager Countess, played by Dame \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/maggie-smith/\" id=\"auto-tag_maggie-smith_1\" data-tag=\"maggie-smith\"\u003eMaggie Smith\u003c/a\u003e. A third movie, set to be released on Sept. 12, 2025, was always going to include a tribute to Smith’s iconic character — but that tribute will now also extend to the actress herself, who \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/news/maggie-smith-dead-downton-abbey-star-dies-obituary-1234587301/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003edied in September 2024 at the age of 89\u003c/a\u003e.\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“The fact that Dame Maggie herself has now passed away since that time, I do think, has given a real added poignancy to a story that we would have planned anyway,” \u003cem\u003eDownton Abbey\u003c/em\u003e executive producer \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/gareth-neame/\" id=\"auto-tag_gareth-neame_1\" data-tag=\"gareth-neame\"\u003eGareth Neame\u003c/a\u003e recently told TVLine while promoting Peacock’s \u003cem\u003eThe Day of the Jackal\u003c/em\u003e. “The loss of the Dowager, it now feels far more significant that you see actors playing characters mourning the family matriarch. But I also see actors mourning the matriarch of the show, and it feels more genuine and more meaningful.”\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-alias=\"cards__inner\" data-component=\"cards-related-content\" data-collapse-to-xs=\"false\" data-layout=\"inline\" data-size=\"md\" data-spacing=\"s-3\" data-cards-spacing=\"s0\"\u003e \u003cdiv data-alias=\"card__inner\" data-post-id=\"1235340577\" data-component=\"card\" data-has-background=\"false\" data-has-overlay=\"false\" data-layout-size=\"xs\" data-layout=\"sidebar\" data-main-alignment=\"s0\" data-main-spacing=\"s0\" data-media-position=\"\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-component=\"image\" data-alias=\"\" data-ratio=\"threeByTwo\" data-round=\"false\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/news/maggie-smith-dead-downton-abbey-cast-tributes-daniel-radcliffe-1235340577/\" title=\"\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"\" data-card-index=\"0\" data-post-id=\"1235340577\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/maggie-smith-dead-downton-abbey-cast-tributes.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\" alt=\"Maggie Smith Dead Downton Abbey Cast Tributes\" height=\"200\" width=\"300\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/maggie-smith-dead-downton-abbey-cast-tributes.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=148%2C100 148w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/maggie-smith-dead-downton-abbey-cast-tributes.jpg?w=300\u0026amp;h=200\u0026amp;crop=1\u0026amp;resize=900%2C600 900w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/